com.jb.couponsystem.entities

Class Coupon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jb.couponsystem.entities.Coupon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity(name="COUPONS")
public class Coupon
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents the coupon entity object. The COUPONS table in the database is generated from this entity, while its attributes form the columns of the table.
    Author:
    Alexander Zablotsky
